'''飓风莱尼'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Lenny}}）是[[信史|有纪录以来]]在11月形成的第二强烈大西洋飓风，也是1999年大西洋飓风季的第12场[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]、第8场飓风和第5场[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|四级飓风]]，于11月13日在西[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]形成，其存在期间一直保持着前所未有的从西向东移动路线。系统于11月15日在[[牙买加|牙买加]]以南达到飓风强度标准，并在接下来数天里先后经过[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]南部和[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]。11月17日，莱尼在加勒比海东北部快速强化，在[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]的[[圣克洛伊岛|圣克洛伊岛]]以南约34公里海域达到每小时250公里的最大风速。飓风在途经[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]期间逐渐减弱，最终于11月23日在[[大西洋|大西洋]]开放海域上空消散。

行经[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]前，莱尼产生的大浪夺走了[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]]北部两人的生命。狂风暴雨导致波多黎各东南部的农作物严重受损。飓风以最高强度从圣克洛伊岛经过，该岛出现大范围洪灾和[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]，但破坏只达到“中等程度”。美属维尔京群岛和波多黎各一共遭受了3.3亿美元（1999年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|330000000|1999}}}}美元）的损失。降雨量最高的是[[法屬聖馬丁|法屬聖馬丁]]的[[国家宪兵|警察局]]，达867毫米。该岛有3人遇难，超过200套物业被毁。附近的[[安提瓜和巴布达|安提瓜和巴布达]]也有1人丧生，暴雨还污染了当地水源。向南远至[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]也受到这场风暴的严重破坏，大浪导致多个城镇和首都之间的联系中断。由于风暴造成了重大损失，其名称“莱尼”因此从大西洋风暴命名名单上退役，以后永远都不会再在[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]命名时使用。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Lenny 1999 track.png}}
飓风莱尼的起源可以追溯到气象部门于11月8日在西南[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]首度发现的一片[[低气压|低气压区]]。之后几天里，其中发展出一片[[对流|对流]]区，但组织结构一直很混乱。低气压区内四处发展出[[雷暴|雷暴]]，给[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]和[[中美洲|中美洲]]部分区域带去暴雨。11月13日，系统的组织性有所改善，当晚经[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]确认，系统已发展出表面环流，[[最大持续风速|风速]]达到每小时55公里。根据这一数据，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]当天下午18点将位于[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]以南约280公里洋面的系统归类成第十六号热带低气压<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = John L. Guiney | date = 1999-12-09 | title = Hurricane Lenny Preliminary Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1999lenny.html | archivedate = 2014-03-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140330144408/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1999lenny.html}}</ref>。低气压中的对流仍然杂乱无章，美国国家飓风中心估计今后3天内系统都不会增强<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles B. Lawrence | date = 1999-11-13 | title = Tropical Depression Sixteen Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902174955/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.001.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.001.html | archivedate = 2013-09-02}}</ref>。这场[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]存在期间一直在沿西[[大西洋|大西洋]]上空一片[[低压槽|低压槽]]的最南端移动，从西向东穿越加勒比海，这一行进方向在[[信史|有纪录以来]]的[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋飓风]]中都是前所未有的<ref name="tcr" />。

系统的组织结构在热带低气压形成后逐渐得到改善<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 1999-11-14 | title = Tropical Depression Sixteen Discussion Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902175004/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.002.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.002.html | archivedate = 2013-09-02}}</ref>，美国国家飓风中心根据飓风猎人的报告将其升级成热带风暴并以“莱尼”（{{lang|en|Lenny}}）命名<ref name="tcr" />。这时气旋的风速已经达到每小时100公里，还有[[风眼|眼状特征]]正在发展<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles B. Lawrence | date = 1999-11-14 | title = Tropical Storm Lenny Special Discussion Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.005.html | archivedate = 2013-09-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902175246/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.005.html}}</ref>。到了{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}11月15日凌晨0点，风暴在[[京斯敦|京斯敦]]西南方向约280公里海域达到飓风强度标准<ref name="tcr" />。这样的快速增强出乎气象部门预料，系统中心此前还爆发出大规模的对流区。升级成飓风同时，莱尼上空发展出[[反气旋|反气旋]]，为飓风发展提供了良好的外部环境<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 1999-11-15 | title = Hurricane Lenny Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2011-07-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902175237/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.007.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.007.html | archivedate = 2013-09-02}}</ref>。风暴发展早期的前进方向大致是东南偏东，到了11月15日则略朝东面转向。飓风猎人报告其中风力时速达到160公里，这已经处于[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | date = 1999-11-15 | title = Hurricane Lenny Discussion Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902175528/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.008.html | archivedate = 2013-09-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.008.html}}</ref>。但在飓风接下来经过[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]以南洋面后，其中的[[风眼|风眼]]已经消失，云层格局的组织结构有所恶化，风速也降至每小时140公里<ref name="tcr" />。美国国家飓风中心指出，云层格局的恶化可能是因“细微的环境变化”对风暴的小规模内核产生干扰所致。经过这次突然的弱化后<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 1999-11-16 | title = Hurricane Lenny Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.011.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902175555/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.011.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-09-02}}</ref>，飓风猎人侦察机报告系统中重新形成了风眼，风力时速也再次达到160公里。气象部门估计飓风东面将会有一片[[高压脊|高压脊]]形成，迫使莱尼向东北方向转向，于24小时后进入[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]<ref name="d12">{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | date = 1999-11-16 | title = Hurricane Lenny Discussion Twelve | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.012.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902175828/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.012.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-09-02}}</ref>。

11月16日，飓风莱尼开始进入为期24小时的[[爆发性增强|爆发性增强]]期，在[[莫纳海峡|莫纳海峡]]以南约265公里海域达到大型飓风强度标准{{#tag:ref|大型飓风指[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]可以在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]中达到三级或以上的风暴<ref name="glos">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml}}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="tcr" />。气旋中发展出层次分明的[[雨带|带状特征]]和良好的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]，从波多黎各[[圣胡安_(波多黎各)|圣胡安]]的雷达上可以清晰地看到其中心的圆形风眼<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 1999-11-16 | title = Hurricane Lenny Discussion Fourteen | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.014.html | archivedate = 2013-09-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902175846/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.014.html}}</ref>。飓风的组织结构继续增强，直径46公里的风眼周围有闭合的风眼墙团团围绕<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 1999-11-16 | title = Hurricane Lenny Discussion Fifteen | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.015.html | archivedate = 2014-09-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902175855/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.015.html}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}11月17日中午12点左右，莱尼在朝加勒比地区东北部群岛逼近期间成为1999年大西洋飓风季的第5场四级飓风，创下单季形成四级飓风数量的新纪录<ref name="tcr" />。接下来飓风从[[毛纳沃|毛纳沃]]东南方向约121公里洋面掠过，这也是系统距离波多黎各最近的一次<ref name="srh" />。此后不久，莱尼在经过[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]的[[圣克洛伊岛|圣克洛伊岛]]以南约33公里海域期间达到风速每小时250公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />，成为有纪录以来在11月形成的第二强大西洋飓风<ref>{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | date = 2009-01-26 | title = Hurricane Paloma Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2011-07-29 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023002459/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL172008_Paloma.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL172008_Paloma.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]]}}</ref>，并且当时还是仅有的4场在11月形成的大型飓风之一<ref name="srh">{{cite report | publisher = San Juan, Puerto Rico National Weather Service Office | title = Preliminary Storm Report on Hurricane Lenny November 16–19 1999 | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131003050623/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/sju/?n=1999_lenny | archivedate = 2013-10-03 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/sju/?n=1999_lenny}}</ref>，不过之后2001年的[[飓风米歇尔|飓风米歇尔]]和[[2008年大西洋飓风季|2008年]]的[[飓风帕洛马|飓风帕洛马]]都在11月达到了这一强度标准<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140730040125/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2013-052714.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2013-052714.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-04-01 | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | archivedate = 2014-07-30}}</ref>。根据飓风猎人的报告，莱尼的最强风速位于气旋的东南部分，报告中还显示系统的最低[[气压|气压]]为933[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.55[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），在24小时里就下降了34毫巴。此外，经降落到风暴表面的[[投落送|投落送]]记录，气旋表面风速高达每小时339公里，这也创下了投落送记录的飓风风速新纪录<ref name="tcr" />。

由于两个高压脊之间存在的弱转向气流影响，莱尼的前进速度在达到最高强度期间有所放缓。虽然外界环境仍然有利于强化，但飓风却在转朝东面方向飘移的过程中出现减弱，这可能是由于[[上升流|上升流]]导致[[海面温度|海面温度]]降低所致。11月18日晚，风暴的风眼进入[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]上空，风力时速仍有205公里。莱尼接下来继续减弱，于次日袭击[[安圭拉|安圭拉]]和[[圣巴泰勒米岛|圣巴泰勒米岛]]。系统转朝东北方向飘移，给加勒比地区东北部[[群岛|群岛]]带去狂风暴雨<ref name="tcr" />。11月19日晚，由于[[风切变|风切变]]增多，气旋的中心从最深层对流中暴露出来，飓风弱化成热带风暴<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 1999-11-19 | title = Tropical Storm Lenny Discussion Twenty-Six | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.026.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902180840/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.026.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-09-02}}</ref>。11月20日，风暴登陆安圭拉<ref name="tcr" />，这时其中心的位置已经难以确定<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles B. Lawrence | date = 1999-11-20 | title = Tropical Storm Lenny Discussion Twenty-Seven | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2013-09-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902180849/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.027.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.027.html}}</ref>。当天晚些时候，气旋离开加勒比<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 1999-11-20 | title = Tropical Storm Lenny Discussion Twenty-Eight | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.028.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902181055/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.028.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-09-02}}</ref>并继续向东北方向前进。11月21日，莱尼转向东北并降级成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。风暴中心渐趋细长，以致于其深层对流已处在中心以东至少160公里外<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 1999-11-21 | title = Tropical Depression Lenny Discussion Thirty-Two | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.032.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130902181310/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/1999/dis/NAL1699.032.html | archivedate = 2013-09-02}}</ref>。11月22日清晨，气旋最后一次向东转向，于次日在小安的列斯群岛以东约1110公里洋面消散<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Lenny_17_nov_1999_2004Z.jpg|thumb]]以南的飓风莱尼]]
[[牙买加|牙买加]]在风暴形成早期收到了[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]和飓风观察预警。之后[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]收到了飓风观察预警，[[多明尼加共和国|多明尼加共和国]]也收到了热带风暴警告<ref name="tcr" />。[[海地|海地]]官员宣布南方3个省进入警戒状态，并拨款约100万美元（1999年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1000000|1999}}}}美元）用作飓风防灾资金<ref name="afp1116">{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | date = 1999-11-16 | title = One death blamed on Hurricane Lenny; still threatens Caribbean | publisher = ReliefWeb | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130914035153/http://reliefweb.int/report/colombia/one-death-blamed-hurricane-lenny-still-threatens-caribbean | archivedate = 2013-09-14 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/colombia/one-death-blamed-hurricane-lenny-still-threatens-caribbean}}</ref>。官员建议海地南部和邻近的多明尼加共和国那些生活在洪水易发地区的居民及时撤离<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Observer-Reporter | date = 1999-11-16 | title = Hurricane Lenny Gains Strength, Threatens Islands | accessdate = 2011-08-14 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=imdeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=M2ENAAAAIBAJ&pg=4198,36084&dq=lenny+jamaica&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200524174131/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=imdeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=M2ENAAAAIBAJ&pg=4198,36084&dq=lenny+jamaica&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ppg">{{cite news | author = Michael Norton | agency = Associated Press | date = 1999-11-14 | title = Late hurricane threatens Haiti, Puerto Rico | newspaper = Pittsburgh Post-Gazette | accessdate = 2011-08-14 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-TAxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KHADAAAAIBAJ&pg=2754,5358583&dq=lenny+tropical+jamaica&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200524174136/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-TAxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KHADAAAAIBAJ&pg=2754,5358583&dq=lenny+tropical+jamaica&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

11月15日晚，波多黎各和[[维尔京群岛|维尔京群岛]]收到了飓风观察预警，并在6小时后升级成飓风警告<ref name="tcr" />。这时气象部门预测莱尼将从波多黎各上空经过<ref name="d12" />。飓风到达距该岛最近的位置后，飓风警告于11月17日降级成热带风暴警告，并于次日和向维尔京群岛发布的公告一起中止<ref name="tcr" />。波多黎各的媒体根据[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻圣胡安办事处发布的声明和警告对飓风实行不间断追踪报道，公众根据这些报道得以充分了解飓风对岛上构成的威胁。约有4700人在风暴来袭前疏散到了191间避难所。这其中有1190位[[庞塞|庞塞]]居民撤离到了27所[[学校|学校]]，还有波多黎各西部生活的584位居民也疏散到了避难所<ref name="is">{{cite news | newspaper = Island Sun | title = NEAC Chairman Looks at Impact of Recent Hurricanes on the BVI | accessdate = 2012-03-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120321145603/http://www.islandsun.com/271199/local5-v3i10.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.islandsun.com/271199/local5-v3i10.html | archivedate = 2012-03-21}}</ref>。政府关闭了所有的学校，并下令禁止销售任何含[[酒精|酒精]]的饮料，还冻结了应急物资的价格<ref name="BBC article">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Lenny threatens Puerto Rico | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/523905.stm | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120316060808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/523905.stm | publisher = BBC | date = 1999-11-17 | archivedate = 2012-03-16 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]启动了6支医疗援助队、3个医疗支援队和两个先行医疗评估组。该机构在美属维尔京群岛的多所学校存放了可供当地居民5天生存所需的食品<ref>{{cite web | author = Federal Emergency Management Agency | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 1999-11-17 | title = FEMA Mobilizes in Response to Hurricane Lenny | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | archivedate = 2013-09-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = http://reliefweb.int/report/puerto-rico-united-states-america/fema-mobilizes-response-hurricane-lenny | url = http://reliefweb.int/node/56776}}</ref>。飓风来袭前，美属维尔京群岛总督查尔斯·韦斯利·特恩布尔（{{lang|en|Charles Wesley Turnbull}}）宣布[[群岛|群岛]]进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Cynthia Long | work = DisasterRelief.org | publisher = ReliefWeb | title = Hurricane Lenny heads for Puerto Rico, Virgin Islands | date = 1999-11-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130918220907/http://reliefweb.int/report/puerto-rico-united-states-america/hurricane-lenny-heads-puerto-rico-virgin-islands | archivedate = 2013-09-18 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2011-10-10 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/puerto-rico-united-states-america/hurricane-lenny-heads-puerto-rico-virgin-islands}}</ref>。圣克洛伊岛有309人在风暴期间躲进避难所<ref name="srh" />。[[英属维尔京群岛|英属维尔京群岛]]官员也开设了8个避难所<ref name="is" />，当地的航空公司和酒店还协助了游客的疏散工作<ref>{{cite web | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 1999-11-16 | title = CDERA Situation Report # 2 - Hurricane Lenny | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131009211945/http://reliefweb.int/report/antigua-and-barbuda/cdera-situation-report-2-hurricane-lenny | archivedate = 2013-10-09 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2011-10-10 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/antigua-and-barbuda/cdera-situation-report-2-hurricane-lenny}}</ref>。

加勒比地区东部的多国政府发布了飓风警告，警告生效范围向南一至延伸到了[[蒙塞拉特岛|蒙塞拉特岛]]<ref name="tcr" />。安圭拉官员建议沿海地区居民撤离。学校在风暴来临前关闭，该岛到圣马丁岛之间的轮渡服务暂时中止，船只也转移到安全地点。[[圣基茨岛|圣基茨岛]]和[[尼维斯|尼维斯]]于11月16日启用国家应急管理机构，当地官员建议生活在水域附近的居民疏散，该国每个区域都开设了避难所。此外，商店延长了营业时间，以便人们囤积物资<ref>{{cite web | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 1999-11-16 | title = Situation Report # 3 - Hurricane Lenny | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/anguilla/situation-report-3-hurricane-lenny | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130829141041/http://reliefweb.int/report/anguilla/situation-report-3-hurricane-lenny | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-08-29}}</ref>。[[安提瓜和巴布达|安提瓜和巴布达]]的大部分商户和学校都在风暴期间关闭，多明尼加也封闭了机场<ref name="ifrc1118">{{cite web | author = International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 1999-11-18 | title = Caribbean Hurricane Lenny Alert | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130903220851/http://reliefweb.int/report/anguilla/caribbean-hurricane-lenny-alert | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/anguilla/caribbean-hurricane-lenny-alert | archivedate = 2013-09-03}}</ref>。更南面的[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]没有收到多少有关这场飓风的警告，大部分居民直接把自己的船只留在水中<ref>{{cite web | author = Peter Coles | year = 2003 | publisher = UNESCO | title = The time of sands... | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | archivedate = 2011-06-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110607041756/http://www.unesco.org/csi/wise/sands.htm | deadurl = no | url = http://www.unesco.org/csi/wise/sands.htm}}</ref>。

